Sharma, Priyanka	  | Engineering Alumni | University of Illinois at Chicago                     It all starts with a single spark         Skip to the content of this page ,  the main menu , the site search form , the site home page .        UIC Logo        Engineering Alumni     Search the site     Toggle Menu      Search                  UIC Logo          Engineering Alumni      Engineering Alumni   Main Menu    News    Expand News menu           Dean's List    RISE Magazine         Events    Expand Events menu           Upcoming Events         Get Involved    Expand Get Involved menu           Join us on LinkedIn    Become a Mentor    Volunteer    Engineer your own involvement    Honor a Professor         Awards    Expand Awards menu           2019 Alumni Award Honorees    2018 Alumni Award Honorees    2017 Alumni Award Honorees         Give    Contact     Eyebrow menu    College of Engineering    Engineering Career Center    UIC menu    UIC.edu    Campus Map       Search                           Priyanka	  Sharma  Outstanding Young Engineer Award   Chemical Engineering               About   Dr. Priyanka Sharma is a co-founder of Kazmira, a manufacturing company which focuses on the large-scale production of botanical extracts from industrial hemp.Dr. Sharma has a bachelors in Chemical Engineering &a Ph.D. in Chemical Engineering, both from the University of Illinois at Chicago.Together, Dr. Sharma and her co-founder Mr. Sharma, manage a team of engineers and scientists at their manufacturing facility in Watkins, CO. Prior to her role at Kazmira, Dr. Sharma completed her doctorate under the supervision of Dr. Sohail Murad at the University of Illinois at Chicago. During this time, Dr. Sharma published multiple journal articles and review article, including one book chapter all focusing on work in molecular modeling of functionalized nanoparticles and their behavior in biological systems. At Kazmira, Dr. Sharma is enthusiastic towards mentoring young engineers and technical operators in building a strong manufacturing team. For Dr. Sharma, an energetic and focused team is the foundation of a successful manufacturing company, one that she hopes to replicate around the world to provide international markets with pure botanical extracts from industrial hemp. Through the dedication of her and Mr.Sharma, they continue to work towards their infinite goal of accelerating the access of industrial hemp derived cannabinoids to the world through premier science and education.                    UIC Logo        Engineering Alumni       Contact   851 S. Morgan - SEO Rm. 811  Phone: 3129969422  MWilli60@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook            UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  Â© 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings                 